::Hot Rod::

He walks pass Prowl.
"I gotta get some CR time. I'll see you all later."
He finds his way to a CR chamber, and gets in.

::Epyon::

He was frustrated that his orders had not been followed. The whole
Starjumper should have been part of the city by now.
"I'll have to bring the parts my self. Beast mode."
He transformes to his dragon mode, and heads towards the StarJumper.

::DrillBit::

He arrived where the map said.
"Apoc, I'm here!"

::KitKat2::

After the initial fight she backs away, waiting for Silver Scout to
attack next.
